00:31:10,020 --> 00:31:11,860
I could only tell him the truth.

559
00:31:12,620 --> 00:31:13,460
Did he believe you?

560
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:15,060
I don't know.

561
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:17,500
I came back yesterday in a blur.

562
00:31:17,620 --> 00:31:19,220
I don't know what he really thinks.

563
00:31:19,740 --> 00:31:21,220
The Crown Prince is very cautious.

564
00:31:21,460 --> 00:31:23,220
I'm sure he'll ask you about it again.

565
00:31:23,900 --> 00:31:26,300
Don't worry. It won't hurt your family.

566
00:31:34,980 --> 00:31:36,100
Douzi.

567
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:38,060
How come

568
00:31:38,060 --> 00:31:40,180
I've never heard you
talk about your mother?

569
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:42,020
My mother?

570
00:31:42,260 --> 00:31:43,100
Which one do you mean?

571
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:44,660
You have several mothers?

572
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:45,700
So many.

573
00:31:46,420 --> 00:31:48,780
I had a Milk Nurse when I was little.

574
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:50,380
She always spanked me.

575
00:31:50,380 --> 00:31:52,660
I called her Mother Zhu.

576
00:31:52,940 --> 00:31:54,100
Then she'd stop hitting me.

577
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:55,660
My First Father

578
00:31:55,660 --> 00:31:56,820
had a lover.

579
00:31:57,460 --> 00:31:59,060
She always did my laundry.

580
00:31:59,540 --> 00:32:01,820
I'd call her Mother Chen.

581
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:04,500
And then there was this Mrs. Zhang

582
00:32:04,620 --> 00:32:06,260
who loved swearing.

583
00:32:06,900 --> 00:32:09,180
She always gave me roast chicken feet.

584
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:12,180
I called her Mother Zhang.

585
00:32:12,860 --> 00:32:14,260
When she got happy,

586
00:32:14,260 --> 00:32:15,660
I'd have chicken feet to eat.

587
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:19,860
I meant

588
00:32:19,860 --> 00:32:21,340
your real mother.

589
00:32:24,660 --> 00:32:27,500
Real mother.

590
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:32,340
I don't have a real mother.

591
00:32:35,060 --> 00:32:37,060
My fathers told me

592
00:32:37,740 --> 00:32:38,980
when I was little,

593
00:32:39,700 --> 00:32:40,620
I was left by someone

594
00:32:40,620 --> 00:32:42,780
in a wooden box in
the middle of nowhere.

595
00:32:44,020 --> 00:32:46,740
I don't know who my parents are.

596
00:32:47,780 --> 00:32:49,020
Do your three fathers

597
00:32:49,500 --> 00:32:50,420
treat you well?

598
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:54,100
Not too bad.

599
00:32:54,740 --> 00:32:59,060
You know,
sometimes we don't have any food.

600
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:00,820
They'd take me to steal some.

601
00:33:03,660 --> 00:33:04,740
I'll be there for you.

602
00:33:04,820 --> 00:33:06,020
You won't have to steal anymore.

603
00:33:08,340 --> 00:33:09,980
Even after we switch back our bodies,

604
00:33:09,980 --> 00:33:11,060
you can stay with me.

605
00:33:11,500 --> 00:33:13,260
I would treat you like my sister.

606
00:33:13,860 --> 00:33:15,340
If you don't like it here in the palace,

607
00:33:15,340 --> 00:33:16,540
I'll send you out.

608
00:33:17,180 --> 00:33:18,220
If you want,

609
00:33:18,220 --> 00:33:19,860
you can stay in my residence forever.

610
00:33:20,020 --> 00:33:22,260
I'll tell my father and mother
to treat you well.

611
00:33:24,940 --> 00:33:26,220
Your residence?

612
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:28,820
I haven't traveled the world yet.

613
00:33:31,860 --> 00:33:32,940
And I wonder

614
00:33:33,380 --> 00:33:35,020
how my fathers are doing now.

615
00:33:44,580 --> 00:33:45,140
This way.

616
00:33:45,420 --> 00:33:46,020
Okay.

617
00:33:47,540 --> 00:33:48,620
Two guys over here.

618
00:33:49,500 --> 00:33:50,380
Coming.

619
00:33:51,060 --> 00:33:51,660
Catch.

620
00:33:53,700 --> 00:33:54,500
Slow down.

621
00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:54,980
Help me.

622
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:55,780
Be careful.

623
00:33:57,740 --> 00:33:58,260
Okay.

624
00:33:58,380 --> 00:33:59,620
Carry this over there with me.

625
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:00,500
All right.

626
00:34:00,500 --> 00:34:01,700
In one, two.

627
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:03,780
Give me a hand.

628
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:04,540
Slowly.

629
00:34:07,380 --> 00:34:08,100
Hurry up.

630
00:34:08,260 --> 00:34:09,420
Don't waste time. Carefully.

631
00:34:09,420 --> 00:34:10,260
Sir.

632
00:34:10,340 --> 00:34:11,020
Sir.

633
00:34:11,420 --> 00:34:12,580
- Peace brings money.
- Hurry up.

634
00:34:13,140 --> 00:34:14,100
Peace brings money.

635
00:34:14,540 --> 00:34:15,180
Hurry up.

636
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:17,300
Slow down.

637
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:18,180
Hand me that.

638
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:19,020
Right.

639
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:21,620
Let's get this up.

640
00:34:21,860 --> 00:34:22,780
Help me.

641
00:34:23,580 --> 00:34:24,540
Stop pretending.

642
00:34:25,980 --> 00:34:27,220
It's so annoying.

643
00:34:28,180 --> 00:34:29,260
You said...

644
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:30,660
We'd see Douzi here.

645
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:31,860
It turned out

646
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:33,500
we didn't even get into the palace.

647
00:34:33,500 --> 00:34:33,900
Well...

648
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:35,540
Stop arguing. Don't worry.

649
00:34:35,900 --> 00:34:37,660
I saw some officers

650
00:34:37,660 --> 00:34:39,100
went over there
with two jars of alcohol.

651
00:34:39,100 --> 00:34:41,220
They're going to get drunk tonight.

652
00:34:41,540 --> 00:34:43,660
Let's take the opportunity to...

653
00:34:43,660 --> 00:34:44,740
Yu, do you mean

654
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:45,540
we escape?

655
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:46,380
Exactly.

656
00:34:47,100 --> 00:34:47,820
Hold on.

657
00:34:48,660 --> 00:34:50,140
We all sleep in a large bunk.

658
00:34:50,340 --> 00:34:51,260
If we get up at midnight,

659
00:34:51,260 --> 00:34:52,780
someone will find out.

660
00:34:53,700 --> 00:34:55,420
I really wonder what you have

661
00:34:55,420 --> 00:34:57,220
in your brain.

662
00:34:57,220 --> 00:34:58,420
If anyone asks,

663
00:34:58,420 --> 00:34:59,980
just say you need to pee.

664
00:34:59,980 --> 00:35:01,340
No one cares about your pee.

665
00:35:02,500 --> 00:35:03,380
We split up.

666
00:35:04,300 --> 00:35:05,820
Wait for my signal.

667
00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:06,860
Someone, come here.

668
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:07,980
Yu, you're right.

669
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:12,540
And over here.

670
00:35:12,540 --> 00:35:13,340
Listen to me.

671
00:35:13,460 --> 00:35:14,260
Tonight,

672
00:35:14,260 --> 00:35:15,780
we do like this...

673
00:35:17,020 --> 00:35:17,780
Come here!

674
00:35:18,060 --> 00:35:19,340
Come on. Try harder.

675
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,980
Move it up.

676
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:29,460
These guys are really suspicious.

677
00:35:30,020 --> 00:35:31,060
- All right.
- Higher here.

678
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:32,460
We stick to the plan.

679
00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:34,180
We set a trap tonight.

680
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:36,180
And then you let everyone

681
00:35:36,620 --> 00:35:38,660
in the Imperial Court know

682
00:35:38,660 --> 00:35:39,940
that they hired some fake refugees.

683
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:41,300
The Crown Prince is in charge of hiring.

684
00:35:41,660 --> 00:35:42,620
When the news gets out,

685
00:35:43,500 --> 00:35:44,660
he will be humiliated.

686
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,460
In the Relief Organization situation,

687
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:48,420
the Crown Prince ordered

688
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:50,100
to raid two officers' houses.

689
00:35:50,540 --> 00:35:53,220
These two officers
worked for Lord Liu Qinyuan.

690
00:35:53,700 --> 00:35:54,980
This time, Lord Liu

691
00:35:55,020 --> 00:35:57,860
has decided to mess
with the Crown Prince.

692
00:36:01,420 --> 00:36:02,660
Come on. Over here.

693
00:36:02,700 --> 00:36:03,420
I got the material.

694
00:36:03,420 --> 00:36:03,980
Let's go.

695
00:36:04,770 --> 00:36:07,300
[Xingqing Hall]

696
00:36:11,740 --> 00:36:12,820
Mei Yushan and I

697
00:36:12,820 --> 00:36:15,340
switched bodies
on the day of the lunar eclipse.

698
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:17,620
The pearl somehow went to the sky

699
00:36:17,620 --> 00:36:19,380
and then it started to shine.

700
00:36:39,870 --> 00:36:43,060
♪It's your mesmerizing glance♪

701
00:36:43,380 --> 00:36:46,650
♪Freezing the gentle breeze
of the mundane world♪

702
00:36:46,710 --> 00:36:52,280
♪Your gentle call awakens me
from my unfinished dreams♪

703
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:55,930
♪It's hard to convey my love for you
when fighting for the homeland♪

704
00:36:55,990 --> 00:36:59,450
♪Our destined encounter♪

705
00:36:59,450 --> 00:37:04,310
♪I am meant to accompany you
on this journey♪

706
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:07,830
♪Wishing for a bit more♪

707
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:11,540
♪So love feels even more real♪

708
00:37:11,540 --> 00:37:17,180
♪You and I, each completing the other,
year after year♪

709
00:37:17,180 --> 00:37:20,200
♪Accompany me to explore the world♪

710
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:23,850
♪We walk together on bustling streets♪

711
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:29,220
♪My heart leans
towards your warm embrace♪

712
00:37:29,420 --> 00:37:36,200
♪We're both kites reclaimed
from the edge of the sky♪

713
00:37:36,330 --> 00:37:41,780
♪If it's an unfathomable fate,
let me do it again♪

714
00:37:41,780 --> 00:37:48,240
♪We're both misunderstood,
yet we accept it willingly♪

715
00:37:48,690 --> 00:37:57,520
♪Step forth boldly and join me
without asking where we're heading♪
